elements.name: Launch the ACS application and login the application ACS_GMR_Import

steps.name: I login with "ACS USER" user given in "Login" sheet ACS_GMR_Import

elements.name: create a direct shipment ACS_GMR_Import single BOE multiple VT and multiple BOE single VT.

steps.name: To verify whether user is able to create Direct Shipment from Add MAWB/HAWB screen ACS_GMR_Import
I login with "ACS AIRLINE KALE" airline user given in "Login" sheet ACS_GMR_Import
user should be able to Approve the Airline DO request from Kale Airline account
logout with airline ane login with FF.
user should be able to do Weight verification of Consol Shipment
user should be able to do Consol DO and assign the shipment to another CB
user should be able to do BoE for Direct/Consol Shipment
user should be able to do Pick Order for Direct/Consol Shipment
user should be able to do OOC for Direct/Consol Shipment
user should be able to BoE ASI and View the ACS Receipt for Direct/Consol Shipment
user should be able to assign the shipment to Consignee to create TSP for Direct/Consol shipment
To check if user is able to create multiple VT for single BoE  from Shipment list page
To verify whether user is able to Cancel the token on click of Cancel Token Button from VCT screen
To check if user is able to create single VT  for multiple BoE  from shipment list page
user should be able to view Complete icon for Dock In/Dock Out on Track and Trace screen when the CTO perform Dock In/Dock Out activity.
To verify whether the user is able to View Partial Complete icon for Dock In/Dock Out on Track and Trace screen when the CTO perform Dock In/Dock Out activity for 1 VT out of 2 VT.
To check whether the system displays proper status for ARR,RCF,NFD,ADO,DI,Consol DO, BoE, RFE,FFE,OOC, TSP,VT,GD with proper date and timestamp.
user should be able tor clicks on AWB number and it should display its  details and correct status in its respective fields.
user should be able to View the Transaction Report From Sub-menu of Reports
user should be able to View the Dwell Time Report From Sub-menu of Reports
user should be able to View the Tonnage Report
user should be able to release and revoke DO in bulk.
